  "title": "HR Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Craft job advertisements and support hiring campaigns</li><li>Screen and interview different candidates </li><li>Match the right people to the right roles​​​​​​​</li></ul><p><strong>Why You’ll Love This Role</strong></p><ul><li>Mentorship and hands-on guidance from experienced recruiters</li><li>Fast and practical exposure</li><li>Incentives, recognition and growth</li></ul><p><strong>Who we are looking for:</strong></p><ul><li>Adaptable and confident communicator </li><li>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma / Degree (any field)</li></ul><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Orchard\n🕗 <strong>Working Schedule: </strong>Monday - Friday, 8:30am - 5:30pm\n💸​​​​​​​ <strong>Duration:</strong> Immediate - 3 months (extendable / convertible!)</p>",
